### Branch Naming
- `feat/clickup-order-tasks`
- `fix/circleci-webhook-endpoint`
- `refactor/codegen-error-handling`

## Environment Configuration

### Required Environment Variables
```env
# Database
MARIADB_ROOT_PASSWORD=secure_password
MARIADB_DATABASE=opencart_db
MARIADB_USER=opencart
MARIADB_PASSWORD=secure_password

# OpenCart
OPENCART_ADMIN_USERNAME=admin
OPENCART_ADMIN_PASSWORD=secure_password
OPENCART_ADMIN_EMAIL=admin@example.com
```

### Integration Settings
```env
# Stored in database via admin panel
CODEGEN_CIRCLECI_PROJECT_SLUG=gh/username/repository
CODEGEN_CLICKUP_LIST_ID=list_id_here
CODEGEN_AUTO_FIX_ENABLED=true
```

